## Summary
This documentation provides a comprehensive guide for creating cohort syncing integrations with Amplitude, covering both list-based and property-based integration types, including configuration of authentication methods, custom fields, API endpoints (list creation, add users, remove users), payload customization, error handling, and the testing/submission process through the Developer Portal.

